ntly only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/error_event\"><code>error</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/load_event\"><code>load</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/loadend_event\"><code>loadend</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/loadstart_event\"><code>loadstart</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/progress_event\"><code>progress</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/readystatechange_event\"><code>readystatechange</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/timeout_event\"><code>timeout</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Herança:</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequestEventTarget\"><code>XMLHttpRequestEventTarget</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Páginas relacionadas a XMLHttpRequest</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/FormData\"><code>FormData</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ProgressEvent\"><code>ProgressEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequestEventTarget\"><code>XMLHttpRequestEventTarget</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"A documentação sobre isto ainda não foi escrita; por favor considere contribuir!\"><code>XMLHttpRequestUpload</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p>O método <strong>XMLHttpRequest.abort()</strong>&nbsp;aborta a requisição se ela&nbsp;já tiver sido enviada. Quando uma requisição é abortada, o seu&nbsp;readyState é modificado para 0 (Desativado), mas o evento&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Document/readystatechange_event\">readystatechange</a> não é disparado.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sitaxe","title":"Sitaxe","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">xhrInstance.abort();</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parâmetros","title":"Parâmetros","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Nenhum.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"retorno","title":"Retorno","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Nenhum.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exemplo","title":"Exemplo","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> xhr <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">XMLHttpRequest</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    method <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"GET\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    url <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"https://developer.mozilla.org/\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nxhr<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">open</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>method<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>url<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nxhr<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">send</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nxhr<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">abort</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"especificações","title":"Especificações","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Especificação</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comentário</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://xhr.spec.whatwg.org/#the-abort()-method\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"The 'XMLHttpRequest' specification\" rel=\" noopener\">XMLHttpRequest</a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Padrão em tempo real</span></td>\n   <td>WHATWG living standard</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect2\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Estamos convertendo nossos dados de compatibilidade para o formato JSON</a></strong>.\n            Esta tabela de compatibilidade ainda usa o formato antigo,\n            pois ainda não convertemos os dados que ela contém.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Descubra como você pode ajudar! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect3\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Dispositivo móvel</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div></div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari (WebKit)</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td>1</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td>5<sup>[1]</sup><br>\n    7</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td>1.2</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Chrome for Android</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td>1.0</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<p>[1] Esse recurso foi implementado através de ActiveXObject ().&nbsp;O Internet Explorer implementa o padrão XMLHttpRequest desde a versão 7.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"veja_também","title":"Veja também","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/Using_XMLHttpRequest\">Usando o&nbsp;XMLHttpRequest</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Sitaxe","id":"sitaxe"},{"text":"Exemplo","id":"exemplo"},{"text":"Especificações","id":"especificações"},{"text":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"Veja também","id":"veja_também"}],"summary":"O método XMLHttpRequest.abort() aborta a requisição se ela já tiver sido enviada. Quando uma requisição é abortada, o seu readyState é modificado para 0 (Desativado), mas o evento readystatechange não é disparado.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"XMLHttpRequest.abort()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"XMLHttpRequest.abort()","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"XMLHttpRequest.abort()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"XMLHttpRequest.abort()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"XMLHttpRequest.abort()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/api/xmlhttprequest/abort","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/api/xmlhttprequest/abort/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API","title":"APIs da Web"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest","title":"XMLHttpRequest"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/abort","title":"XMLHttpRequest.abort()"}],"pageTitle":"XMLHttpRequest.abort() - APIs da Web | MDN","noIndexing":false}}